                     Ten Popular Soleau Software Games


Game                             Type                   Requires
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Ant Run                : Arcade Puzzle Strategy Game     EGA/VGA & Mouse
Bolo Adventures III    : Logic Puzzle Strategy Maze Game EGA/VGA
Bolo Ball              : Marble Arcade Maze Game         EGA/VGA
Crusher Castle II      : Strategy Adventure Maze Game    EGA/VGA
FaceTrex               : Logic Puzzle Grid Game          EGA/VGA
Ladder Man III         : Logic Animated Puzzle Game      EGA/VGA
