ANT RUN                 Requires EGA/VGA & Mouse          
Race against the clock as you rotate tunnels for the ant to run through.
Quick thinking and fast reflexes are required to keep the ant scurrying
through the Ant Hill passageways. Gain extra points for bonus tunnels and
other objects as you try for the Top Ten High Scores. Keep your ant on the
move with various strategies for really high scores. Warning VERY ADDICTIVE!


BOLO ADVENTURES III     Requires EGA/VGA           
The ultimate Bolo Adventure contains some of the most mind-boggling puzzles
of the entire series. Bolo Adventures is a challenging strategy game where
the objective is to get Mr. Bolo out of 30 devilish puzzles by literally
constructing your own escape. Each room is filled with obstacles such as
lasers, crates, water and boxes and more! A must for all serious gamers.
Great Animated Graphics!  All solutions provided.


BOLO BALL               Requires EGA/VGA
Play against the computer or a friend in this strategy marble maze game.  
Your objective is to get your marbles to the bottom of a maze filled 
with ramps, walls, black holes and much more! Block your opponent by 
pushing your marbles into strategic positions to stop him from doing 
the same to you. In Boloball, there are no clocks, monsters to shoot  
or luck involved.  It's just a pure ADDICTIVE strategy game for the
whole family to enjoy again and again!


CRUSHER CASTLE II       Requires EGA/VGA
Crusher Castle II is an adventure, strategy, and arcade game all in one. 
Your objective is to escape from a haunted castle of 25 rooms filled with 
ghosts, bombs, candles, maps, and much more.  Search the for different 
object to help you escape, but watch out for the roaming ghosts! Packed 
with features and with animated graphics, no two adventures are ever 
the same!  Very few have escaped the Castle...can you ?  
Crusher Castle II is fun for ALL ages!


FACETREX                Requires EGA/VGA
FaceTrex is a challenging and pure strategy logic game where the 
objective is to use your animated man to push faces located on a 12x8
grid board onto their negative image located elsewhere on the board. 
The face grids will slide in the direction pushed until they hit
either another face grid or the side of the board, or special arrow 
grids which re-direct the push. There are 50 mind-bending puzzles 
included with the solutions to all if you get stuck!  A pure problem
solving game for young and old.  Addictive!!!

LADDER MAN III          Requires EGA/VGA
Soleau Software continues the Ladder Man Series with this new release. 
Help Ladder Man collect all the light bulbs in each of the 30 puzzle 
rooms and then reach the elusive doorway. Use his ladder to get to
objects like TNT, boats, crates, balloons and much more, while avoiding 
deadly lasers and dangerous water hazards. You must literally construct 
your escape.  All solutions included if you need them.  A CHALLENGE!!!

LOADER LARRY            Requires EGA/VGA                 
Larry Lontrose is a part-time dock loader in his hometown of Longview.
He has ambitions to be promoted up the corporate ladder. By solving the
40 mind-bending puzzle rooms, you can help Loader Larry fulfill his
dreams. Each room has objects like boxes, balloons, TNT, and much more!
Using these objects and avoiding others, he must reach the doors
located in each room. Loader Larry is pure strategy and logic solving
fun!  All the solutions provided!


MICE MEN                Requires EGA/VGA                      
Soleau Software has created another exciting fun-filled
animated strategy logic game. Try to push and pull columns
of cheese blocks to get your mice to the other end of the
maze before your computer opponent (or friend). Mice Men is packed
with features and written in stunning animated EGA/VGA graphics. 
It's a addicting logic strategy game for the whole family. Mice Men 
allows for two human players to compete. It's funny and fun!


ROCK MAN                Requires EGA/VGA                          
Rock Man is an exciting logic strategy game from Soleau Software. Use 
your ingenuity to help Rock Man collect all the rare moths flying around 
each of the 30 mind-bending mountain puzzles. Use ropes, axes and 
other objects while avoiding dangerous Lava rocks. Packed with features! 
Do you have what it takes solve each puzzle ?  A pure animated logic 
puzzle for both young and old with all solutions included.


WORDMAX                 Requires EGA/VGA & Hard Disk                  
WordMax is another challenging word game from Soleau Software. The objective
is to spell as many words as possible from letters that make up a master
word. The game comes packed with features and has custom scorecards, custom
dictionary options and much more. WordMax has its own dictionary of over 
80,000 words. The game will provide hours of entertainment for all ages!


